data.description: Beautifully Remodeled, Move In Ready Home in an Amazing Location!!!  Enjoy the Florida Room with Over 100 sq ft of EXTRA SPACE Not Included in the Square Footage Listed Above.  Updates in 2020 include: NEW WINDOWS, NEW HVAC, NEW HOT WATER TANK, NEW TILE FLOORING, NEW KITCHEN COUNTER TOPS, SINK, FAUCET, BACK SPLASH, BATHROOMS BOTH REMODELED. Updates in 2021 Include: NEW DISHWASHER, INTERIOR PAINT, BLINDS, LIGHT FIXTURES, and New Plumbing Cleanout in 2023. The home boasts ceiling fans in almost every room, The kitchen is complete with canned lighting, lots of cabinet space. Don't forget the convenience of having the inside utility/laundry room as well! The primary bedroom has plenty of space, a walk-in closet and updated bathroom. East Access to Tinker Air Force Base. Large Backyard and Front Yard.  Partially Wood with Mostly Vinyl Fencing.
